The Five Houston Center app provides high-tech convenience from the palm of your hand. This app streamlines standard building processes and manages everything that takes place within the property. Plus, offers articles and updates on what is happening around downtown Houston.

This innovative solution provides FIVE HC Tenants a platform to navigate building amenities in one place.

Features include:
•Building Events & Announcements
•Bluetooth digital access card
•Building Visitor Registration
•Conference Room Reservations
•Overtime Air Scheduling
•Fitness Center Updates and Waiver Form
•Work Order System Link
•Property Management & Security Contacts
